    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Charadrahyla (Anura: Hylidae) from the cloud forest of western Oaxaca, Mexico" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623750>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623754>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623752>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623756> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623750>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Specimens in life of C haradrahyla sakbah. (A) male holotype (IBH 30989). (B) male paratype (IBH 30990). (C) Female paratype (IBH 30992). (D) Female paratype (IBH 30993). (E) Female paratype (IBH 30994). (F) Enlarged vent tubercles in ventral view of C. sakbah of male holotype (IBH 30989) in life." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623750/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623754>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dorsal (A) and ventral view (B) of the preserved holotype of Charadrahyla sakbah. (C) Ventral aspect of hand and (D) foot of male holotype (IBH 30989)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623754/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623752>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Morphological characters of Charadrahyla sakbah. (A) Axillary membrane of male holotype (IBH 30989). (B) Axillary membrane of female paratype (IBH 30992). (C) Retracted and (D) extended hypertrophied webbing in male holotype (IBH 30989). (E) Nuptial excrescences in dorsal view and (F) view of the palm of the hand without nuptial excrescences in Finger I in male holotype (IBH 30989)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623752/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623756>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. (A) A female (not collected) of C. sakbah in the riverside. (B) Panoramic view of the Chite ku'e river. (C) Typical pool and waterfall where C. sakbah individuals are usually found." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623756/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

